A simple web app that lets users search for recipes by ingredient using **TheMealDB API**.

## Features
- Search for meals by ingredient name.
- View meal images and names.
- Click a meal to see ingredients and instructions.
- Close button stays visible while scrolling.

## Technology Stack
- HTML
- CSS
- JavaScript (Fetch API)
- TheMealDB API (no key required)

## How to Run
1. Open `index.html` in your browser.
2. Type an ingredient (e.g., "chicken", "egg", "tomato").
3. Click **Search** to view meals.

## API Reference
- https://www.themealdb.com/api/json/v1/1/filter.php?i={ingredient}
- https://www.themealdb.com/api/json/v1/1/lookup.php?i={mealId}
